        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks GRG for his gift [<hi rend="italic">A list of the genera of birds</hi> (1840)] and trusts that now GRG will be able to finish John Gould’s MS for <hi rend="italic">Zoology</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
